{
  "stem": "10181.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And she had to take care of her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So that's when we left the second time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We left and go to-- to go to Dinxperlo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was just a very short interlude.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Maybe a few months, I don't know exactly the-- the time span.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And this cousin died, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "She had a-- like a tumor on the brain I think it was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was a form of cancer, I guess.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And she died in the end of 1940, I think it was already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And then this-- the aunt after that went-- went into hiding together with the other-- my other cousin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You know, they never-- she didn't return to the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She lived in that house while-- while my cousin was in the-- in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But after that, they went into hiding.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So that's why we never went back to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't-- they didn't hide in Gennep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They hid somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know exactly where because they--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Apparently, he wanted to see his sick child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the-- the hospital, some of the nurses who were-- who were trustworthy-- not everybody could you could trust-- arranged for him to visit her at night to see her.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he did visit her several times in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was in the private room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they saw her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they also saw her before she died.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is 1941 already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is where you see those Red Cross letters where my mother asked, how come you-- what are you-- how come you're now in Dinxperlo?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when my aunt wrote back to them that we are now staying there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Didn't give the reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
